name: ng-jhipster

scripts.build: npm run cleanup && npm run ngc && webpack && shx cp bundles/ng-jhipster.umd.js bundles/index.js
scripts.build:aot: npm run cleanup && npm run ngc-aot && webpack && shx cp bundles/ng-jhipster.umd.js bundles/index.js
scripts.build:local: npm run build && npm test && npm pack
scripts.cleanup: rimraf src/*.d.ts src/**/*.d.ts src/*.js src/**/*.js aot/* tests/**/*.d.ts tests/**/*.js tests/*.d.ts tests/*.js
scripts.release: npm test && git push && git push --tags && npm publish
scripts.release:major: npm run build && npm version major -a -m "Update to %s" && npm run release
scripts.release:minor: npm run build && npm version minor -a -m "Update to %s" && npm run release
scripts.release:patch: npm run build && npm version patch -a -m "Update to %s" && npm run release
